x\:"Cartwheel illusion on the horizontal axis\: the image squishes and reveals its vertical mirror as the "back face""))' \
'--fps=[Frames per second for the --rotate spin animation (default\: 8)]:FPS:_default' \
'-I+[Path to the JSON index file (overrides config file setting)]:INDEX:_default' \
'--index=[Path to the JSON index file (overrides config file setting)]:INDEX:_default' \
'-d[Enable Floyd-Steinberg dithering for smoother gradients]' \
'--dither[Enable Floyd-Steinberg dithering for smoother gradients]' \
